{"tid":2396941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布林肯與楊潔篪通電話　強調續捍衛新疆西藏香港人權","createTime":"2021-02-06T04:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T16:40:24.000Z","uid":51271,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e91b7b7028e5c5b8ddad27283e5359968a8d8d05","tid":2396941,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574449-20210206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574449-20210206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=4a7cb96f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574449-20210206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=031cb781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574449-20210206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿布林肯與中共中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪通電話。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發表聲明，指布林肯向楊潔篪強調，美國將繼續捍衛包括新疆、西藏與香港在內的人權和民主價值，並敦促中國與國際社會一起，譴責緬甸的軍事政變。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯重申，華府將會與盟友及夥伴捍衛共同價值和利益，要求中國為威脅包括台海在內的印太地區穩定，並損害基於規則的國際體系行為負責。"},{"pid":"bea67aebfeaea51801c827bd2f689876ffb5f12b","tid":2396941,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SecBlinken/status/1357886400675393537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecBlinken%2Fstatus%2F1357886400675393537&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=e9a61acb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecBlinken%2Fstatus%2F1357886400675393537&h=57d5d90b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SecBlinken/status/1357886400675393537</a><br />\n<br />\nIn my call with my counterpart in Beijing, Yang Jiechi, I made clear the U.S. will defend our national interests, stand up for our democratic values, and hold Beijing accountable for its abuses of the international system."},{"pid":"534f6d55f445eca3c55f0d00138a8245f1b41d0e","tid":2396941,"uid":153781,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"唔好話我睇穿佢 真係得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係共和黨做咗有樣嘢好耐"},{"pid":"bf5a1ebcac57391acd4fe7da4d50502ed0e8ebb2","tid":2396941,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"534f6d55f445eca3c55f0d00138a8245f1b41d0e","tid":2396941,"uid":153781,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"唔好話我睇穿佢 真係得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係共和黨做咗有樣嘢好耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"用"},{"pid":"814ee45995315f1b9c4f666ef056ad9b81bc321c","tid":2396941,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:37:25.000Z","msg":"講"},{"pid":"7517c84bacdb6cbdc6124ffc238186cb8f2ef213","tid":2396941,"uid":51271,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"534f6d55f445eca3c55f0d00138a8245f1b41d0e","tid":2396941,"uid":153781,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"唔好話我睇穿佢 真係得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係共和黨做咗有樣嘢好耐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:39:46.000Z","msg":"共和黨連電話都唔會講，繼續放你入SDN LIST"},{"pid":"d2dda661f799023727fae5691171a8f80fea06b3","tid":2396941,"uid":183758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:41:43.000Z","msg":"民主黨班垃圾真係冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n壞事做盡 又竊國"},{"pid":"064179413876880ee727381465f55c81eaefedc2","tid":2396941,"uid":11454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"愈同人講會做野=愈唔會做<br />\nAction speak louder than words <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec97a36d6a18259dce36698e3a69d4169e555a2","tid":2396941,"uid":592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-0